    {
      "id": "PopularPost360550",
      "post_content": "@Roy1138 / pumaman83: Not counterspell, use [Mana Tithe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mana Tithe)!  \n  \nThat said, this card sucks, though there is nothing *strictly* better... there are other options:  \n[Tower Defense](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tower Defense) is a much better option... though it's in {G}  \n[Shield Wall](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Shield Wall) provides a smaller, more reliable boost without the condition.  \n[Steadfastness](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Steadfastness) gives the +0/+3 but is at sorcery speed..which kind of defeats the whole point of a combat trick",
      "posted_by": "tcollins",
